                                    children: [parseFloat(n.shippingCost).toFixed(2), " €"]
                                })]
                            }), e.jsx(wa, {}), e.jsxs("div", {
                                className: "flex justify-between font-semibold text-lg",
                                children: [e.jsx("span", {
                                    children: "Total"
                                }), e.jsxs("span", {
                                    children: [parseFloat(n.total).toFixed(2), " €"]
                                })]
                            })]
                        })]
                    }), e.jsxs($, {
                        children: [e.jsx(ne, {
                            children: e.jsx(ae, {
                                children: "Estado del pedido"
                            })
                        }), e.jsxs(V, {
                            className: "space-y-3",
                            children: [e.jsxs("div", {
                                className: "flex items-center gap-2",
                                children: [e.jsx("div", {
                                    className: "w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full"
                                }), e.jsx("span", {
                                    className: "text-sm",
                                    children: "Pedido confirmado"
                                })]
                            }), e.jsxs("div", {
                                className: "flex items-center gap-2",
                                children: [e.jsx("div", {
                                    className: "w-2 h-2 bg-yellow-500 rounded-full"
                                }), e.jsx("span", {
                                    className: "text-sm",
                                    children: "En proceso"
                                })]
                            }), e.jsxs("div", {
                                className: "flex items-center gap-2",
                                children: [e.jsx("div", {
                                    className: "w-2 h-2 bg-gray-300 rounded-full"
                                }), e.jsx("span", {
                                    className: "text-sm text-gray-500",
                                    children: "Enviado"
                                })]
                            }), e.jsxs("div", {
                                className: "flex items-center gap-2",
                                children: [e.jsx("div", {
                                    className: "w-2 h-2 bg-gray-300 rounded-full"
                                }), e.jsx("span", {
                                    className: "text-sm text-gray-500",
                                    children: "Entregado"
                                })]
                            })]
                        })]
                    }), e.jsxs("div", {
                        className: "space-y-3",
                        children: [e.jsxs(_, {
                            onClick: () => r("/"),
                            variant: "outline",
                            className: "w-full",
                            children: [e.jsx(Nr, {
                                className: "w-4 h-4 mr-2"
                            }), "Volver al catálogo"]
                        }), e.jsx(_, {
                            onClick: () => window.print(),
                            variant: "outline",
                            className: "w-full",
                            children: "Imprimir pedido"
                        })]
                    })]
                })]
            })]
        })
    })
}
const lG = Me.object({
        identifier: Me.string().min(3, "Ingresa un email o nombre de usuario válido"),
        password: Me.string().min(6, "La contraseña debe tener al menos 6 caracteres")
    }),
    cG = () => {
        const {login: t, isLoading: s} = ks(),
            [, r] = mt(),
            n = un({
                resolver: Cn(lG),
                defaultValues: {
                    identifier: "",
                    password: ""
                }
            }),
            a = async i => {
                try {
                    if (!i.identifier || !i.password) {
                        n.setError("identifier", {
                            message: "Usuario y contraseña son requeridos"
                        }),
                        n.setError("password", {
                            message: "Usuario y contraseña son requeridos"
                        });
                        return
                    }
                    const o = await t(i.identifier, i.password);
                    o.success ? o.shouldRedirect ? (console.log("🔄 Redirigiendo admin a dashboard via SPA..."), r("/admin/dashboard")) : r("/") : (n.setError("identifier", {
                        message: o.message || "Usuario o contraseña incorrectos"
                    }), n.setError("password", {
                        message: o.message || "Usuario o contraseña incorrectos"
                    }))
                } catch (o) {
                    console.error("Error en el formulario de login:", o),
                    n.setError("identifier", {
                        message: "Error de conexión. Intente nuevamente."
                    }),
                    n.setError("password", {
                        message: "Error de conexión. Intente nuevamente."
                    })
                }

    mG = Me.object({

    pG = ({user: t, updateProfile: s}) => {

    xG = ({user: t, updateProfile: s, provinces: r}) => {
        const [n, a] = h.useState(!1),
            i = un({
                resolver: Cn(hG),
                defaultValues: {
                    address: (t == null ? void 0 : t.address) || "",
                    city: (t == null ? void 0 : t.city) || "",

                    province: (t == null ? void 0 : t.province) || ""
                }

            o = async l => {

                        title: "Dirección actualizada",

                        title: "Error",

                                        children: "Ciudad"
                                    }), e.jsx(Je, {

                                            placeholder: "Ciudad",
                                            ...l
                                        })
                                    }), e.jsx(nt, {})]
                                })
                            }), e.jsx(tt, {
                                control: i.control,
                                name: "province",
                                render: ({field: l}) => e.jsxs(Xe, {
                                    children: [e.jsx(st, {
                                        children: "Provincia"
                                    }), e.jsxs(He, {
                                        onValueChange: l.onChange,
                                        value: l.value,
                                        children: [e.jsx(Je, {
                                            children: e.jsx(Ue, {
                                                children: e.jsx(We, {
                                                    placeholder: "Selecciona provincia"
                                                })
                                            })
                                        }), e.jsx(Be, {
                                            children: r.map(c => e.jsx(Q, {
                                                value: c.name,
                                                children: c.name
                                            }, c.id))
                                        })]
                                    }), e.jsx(nt, {})]
                                })
                            }), e.jsx(tt, {
                                control: i.control,
                                name: "postalCode",
                                render: ({field: l}) => e.jsxs(Xe, {
                                    children: [e.jsx(st, {
                                        children: "Código postal"
                                    }), e.jsx(Je, {
                                        children: e.jsx(J, {
                                            placeholder: "Código postal",
                                            ...l
                                        })
                                    }), e.jsx(nt, {})]
                                })
                            })]
                        }), e.jsx(_, {
                            type: "submit",
                            disabled: n,
                            className: "w-full md:w-auto",
                            children: n ? e.jsxs(e.Fragment, {
                                children: ["Guardando...", e.jsx(Xt, {
                                    className: "ml-2 h-4 w-4 animate-spin"
                                })]
                            }) : "Guardar dirección"
                        })]
                    })
                })
            })]
        })
    };
function cM(t, s) {
    return function() {
        return t.apply(s, arguments)
    }
}

function BK(t, s, r) {

    }

class Yo {
    constructor(s)
    {
        this.defaults = s || {},
        this.interceptors = {
            request: new q1,
            response: new q1
        }
    }
    async request(s, r)
    {
        try {
            return await this._request(s, r)
        } catch (n) {
            if (n instanceof Error) {
                let a = {};
                Error.captureStackTrace ? Error.captureStackTrace(a) : a = new Error;
                const i = a.stack ? a.stack.replace(/^.+\n/, "") : "";
                try {
                    n.stack ? i && !String(n.stack).endsWith(i.replace(/^.+\n.+\n/, "")) && (n.stack += `
`
                    + i) : n.stack = i
                } catch {}
            }
            throw n
        }
    }
    _request(s, r)
    {
        typeof s == "string" ? (r = r || {}, r.url = s) : r = s || {},
        r = ml(this.defaults, r);
        const {transitional: n, paramsSerializer: a, headers: i} = r;
        n !== void 0 && Lh.assertOptions(n, {
            silentJSONParsing: ia.transitional(ia.boolean),
            forcedJSONParsing: ia.transitional(ia.boolean),
            clarifyTimeoutError: ia.transitional(ia.boolean)
        }, !1),
        a != null && (ce.isFunction(a) ? r.paramsSerializer = {
            serialize: a
        } : Lh.assertOptions(a, {
            encode: ia.function,
            serialize: ia.function
        }, !0)),
        r.allowAbsoluteUrls !== void 0 || (this.defaults.allowAbsoluteUrls !== void 0 ? r.allowAbsoluteUrls = this.defaults.allowAbsoluteUrls : r.allowAbsoluteUrls = !0),
        Lh.assertOptions(r, {
            baseUrl: ia.spelling("baseURL"),
            withXsrfToken: ia.spelling("withXSRFToken")
        }, !0),
        r.method = (r.method || this.defaults.method || "get").toLowerCase();
        let o = i && ce.merge(i.common, i[r.method]);
        i && ce.forEach(["delete", "get", "head", "post", "put", "patch", "common"], g => {
            delete i[g]
        }),
        r.headers = Hr.concat(o, i);
        const l = [];
        let c = !0;
        this.interceptors.request.forEach(function(x) {
            typeof x.runWhen == "function" && x.runWhen(r) === !1 || (c = c && x.synchronous, l.unshift(x.fulfilled, x.rejected))
        });
        const d = [];
        this.interceptors.response.forEach(function(x) {
            d.push(x.fulfilled, x.rejected)
        });
        let u,
            m = 0,
            f;
        if (!c) {
            const g = [X1.bind(this), void 0];
            for (g.unshift.apply(g, l), g.push.apply(g, d), f = g.length, u = Promise.resolve(r); m < f;)
                u = u.then(g[m++], g[m++]);
            return u
        }

        for (m = 0; m < f;) {
            const g = l[m++],
                x = l[m++];
            try {
                y = g(y)
            } catch (b) {
                x.call(this, b);
                break
            }
        }
        try {
            u = X1.call(this, y)
        } catch (g) {
            return Promise.reject(g)
        }
        for (m = 0, f = d.length; m < f;)
            u = u.then(d[m++], d[m++]);

    }
    getUri(s)
    {
        s = ml(this.defaults, s);
        const r = EM(s.baseURL, s.url, s.allowAbsoluteUrls);

}

class pb {
    constructor(s)
    {
        if (typeof s != "function")
            throw new TypeError("executor must be a function.");
        let r;
        this.promise = new Promise(function(i) {
            r = i
        });
        const n = this;
        this.promise.then(a => {
            if (!n._listeners)
                return;
            let i = n._listeners.length;
            for (; i-- > 0;)
                n._listeners[i](a);
            n._listeners = null
        }),
        this.promise.then = a => {
            let i;
            const o = new Promise(l => {
                n.subscribe(l),
                i = l
            }).then(a);
            return o.cancel = function() {
                n.unsubscribe(i)
            }, o
        },
        s(function(i, o, l) {
            n.reason || (n.reason = new rd(i, o, l), r(n.reason))
        })
    }
    throwIfRequested()
    {
        if (this.reason)
            throw this.reason
    }
    subscribe(s)
    {
        if (this.reason) {
            s(this.reason);
            return
        }
        this._listeners ? this._listeners.push(s) : this._listeners = [s]
    }
    unsubscribe(s)
    {
        if (!this._listeners)
            return;
        const r = this._listeners.indexOf(s);
        r !== -1 && this._listeners.splice(r, 1)
    }
    toAbortSignal()
    {
        const s = new AbortController,
            r = n => {
                s.abort(n)
            };
        return this.subscribe(r), s.signal.unsubscribe = () => this.unsubscribe(r), s.signal
    }
    static source()
    {
        let s;
        return {
            token: new pb(function(a) {
                s = a
            }),
            cancel: s
        }
    }
}

                                            children: n.success ? e.jsx("span", {
                                                className: "text-green-600",
                                                children: "✓ Vehículo encontrado"
                                            }) : e.jsx("span", {
                                                className: "text-red-600",
                                                children: "✗ No se encontró ningún vehículo"
                                            })
                                        }), n.success && n.matchedVehicle && e.jsxs("div", {
                                            className: "mt-4 space-y-2",
                                            children: [e.jsxs("p", {
                                                children: [e.jsx("span", {
                                                    className: "font-semibold",
                                                    children: "ID:"
                                                }), " ", n.matchedVehicle.id]
                                            }), e.jsxs("p", {
                                                children: [e.jsx("span", {
                                                    className: "font-semibold",
                                                    children: "Marca:"
                                                }), " ", n.matchedVehicle.marca]
                                            }), e.jsxs("p", {
                                                children: [e.jsx("span", {
                                                    className: "font-semibold",
                                                    children: "Modelo:"
                                                }), " ", n.matchedVehicle.modelo]
                                            }), e.jsxs("p", {
                                                children: [e.jsx("span", {
                                                    className: "font-semibold",
                                                    children: "Versión:"
                                                }), " ", n.matchedVehicle.version]
                                            }), e.jsxs("p", {
                                                children: [e.jsx("span", {
                                                    className: "font-semibold",
                                                    children: "Año:"
                                                }), " ", n.matchedVehicle.anyo]
                                            }), n.totalMatches > 1 && e.jsxs("p", {
                                                className: "text-blue-600",
                                                children: [e.jsx("span", {
                                                    className: "font-semibold",
                                                    children: "Nota:"
                                                }), " Se encontraron ", n.totalMatches, " vehículos que coinciden. Se muestra el primero."]
                                            })]
                                        }), !n.success && e.jsx("p", {
                                            className: "mt-2",
                                            children: "No se encontró ningún vehículo que coincida con los criterios proporcionados."
                                        })]
                                    }), e.jsxs("div", {
                                        children: [e.jsx("p", {
                                            className: "text-sm font-semibold mb-1",
                                            children: "Datos de respuesta completos:"
                                        }), e.jsx("pre", {
                                            className: "p-2 bg-gray-100 rounded-md overflow-auto text-xs",
                                            children: JSON.stringify(n, null, 2)
                                        })]
                                    })]
                                }) : e.jsx("div", {
                                    className: "flex justify-center items-center h-48 text-gray-400",
                                    children: "Aquí se mostrarán los resultados del matching"
                                })
                            })]
                        })]
                    })]
                })
            }), e.jsx(ze, {
                value: "part-matching",
                children: e.jsxs("div", {
                    className: "border-t pt-4",
                    children: [e.jsx("p", {
                        className: "mb-6 text-gray-600",

                    }), e.jsxs("div", {
                        className: "grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6",
                        children: [e.jsxs($, {
                            children: [e.jsxs(ne, {
                                children: [e.jsx(ae, {
                                    children: "Matching de Pieza"
                                }), e.jsx(Bt, {
                                    children: "Introduce el ID de una pieza para encontrar vehículos compatibles"
                                })]
                            }), e.jsx(V, {
                                children: e.jsx("form", {
                                    onSubmit: j,
                                    className: "space-y-4",
                                    children: e.jsxs("div", {
                                        className: "space-y-2",
                                        children: [e.jsx(q, {

                                            children: "ID de Pieza"
                                        }), e.jsx(J, {
                                            id: "partId",
                                            name: "partId",
                                            type: "number",
                                            value: m,
                                            onChange: g,
                                            placeholder: "Ejemplo: 1234"
                                        }), e.jsx("p", {
                                            className: "text-sm text-gray-500",
                                            children: "El sistema buscará vehículos compatibles basados en los campos de matching de la pieza (codVersion, puertas, anyoInicio, anyoFin, rvCode)."
                                        })]
                                    })
                                })
                            }), e.jsx(Pa, {
                                className: "flex justify-end",
                                children: e.jsx(_, {
                                    onClick: j,
                                    disabled: s,
                                    children: s ? "Buscando..." : "Buscar vehículos compatibles"
                                })
                            })]
                        }), e.jsxs($, {
                            children: [e.jsxs(ne, {
                                children: [e.jsx(ae, {
                                    children: "Vehículos Compatibles"
                                }), e.jsx(Bt, {
                                    children: "Aquí se mostrarán los vehículos compatibles con la pieza"
                                })]
                            }), e.jsx(V, {
                                children: i ? e.jsxs("div", {
                                    className: "space-y-4",
                                    children: [e.jsxs("div", {
                                        className: "p-4 rounded-md bg-gray-50",
                                        children: [e.jsx("p", {
                                            className: "font-semibold",
                                            children: i.success ? e.jsxs("span", {
                                                className: "text-green-600",
                                                children: ["✓ Se encontraron ", i.count, " vehículos compatibles"]
                                            }) : e.jsx("span", {
                                                className: "text-red-600",
                                                children: "✗ No se encontraron vehículos compatibles"
                                            })
                                        }), i.success && i.data && i.data.length > 0 && e.jsxs("div", {
                                            className: "mt-4",
                                            children: [e.jsx("p", {
                                                className: "font-semibold mb-2",
                                                children: "Vehículos compatibles:"
                                            }), e.jsx("div", {
                                                className: "max-h-64 overflow-y-auto",
                                                children: i.data.map((v, N) => e.jsxs("div", {
                                                    className: "mb-4 p-3 bg-white rounded border border-gray-200",
                                                    children: [e.jsxs("p", {
                                                        className: "text-sm text-gray-500",
                                                        children: ["Vehículo #", N + 1]
                                                    }), e.jsxs("p", {
                                                        children: [e.jsx("span", {
                                                            className: "font-semibold",
                                                            children: "ID:"
                                                        }), " ", v.id]
                                                    }), e.jsxs("p", {
                                                        children: [e.jsx("span", {
                                                            className: "font-semibold",
                                                            children: "Marca:"
                                                        }), " ", v.marca]
                                                    }), e.jsxs("p", {
                                                        children: [e.jsx("span", {
                                                            className: "font-semibold",
                                                            children: "Modelo:"
                                                        }), " ", v.modelo]
                                                    }), e.jsxs("p", {
                                                        children: [e.jsx("span", {
                                                            className: "font-semibold",
                                                            children: "Versión:"
                                                        }), " ", v.version]
                                                    }), e.jsxs("p", {
                                                        children: [e.jsx("span", {
                                                            className: "font-semibold",
                                                            children: "Año:"
                                                        }), " ", v.anyo]
                                                    })]
                                                }, v.id))
                                            })]
                                        }), !i.success && e.jsx("p", {
                                            className: "mt-2",
                                            children: "No se encontraron vehículos compatibles con la pieza proporcionada."
                                        })]
                                    }), e.jsxs("div", {
                                        children: [e.jsx("p", {
                                            className: "text-sm font-semibold mb-1",
                                            children: "Datos de respuesta completos:"
                                        }), e.jsx("pre", {
                                            className: "p-2 bg-gray-100 rounded-md overflow-auto text-xs",
                                            children: JSON.stringify(i, null, 2)
                                        })]
                                    })]
                                }) : e.jsx("div", {
                                    className: "flex justify-center items-center h-48 text-gray-400",
                                    children: "Aquí se mostrarán los vehículos compatibles"
                                })
                            })]
                        })]
                    })]
                })
            })]
        })]
    })
}
function WK() {
    const [t, s] = h.useState(null),
        [r, n] = h.useState(!0);
    return h.useEffect(() => {
        (async () => {
            try {
                console.log("TEST: Cargando módulos de pago...");
                const i = await fetch("/api/admin/payment-modules");
                console.log("TEST: Response status:", i.status),
                console.log("TEST: Response ok:", i.ok);
                const o = await i.json();
                console.log("TEST: Data received:", o),
                console.log("TEST: Data type:", typeof o),
                console.log("TEST: Is array?", Array.isArray(o)),
                Array.isArray(o) && (console.log("TEST: Data length:", o.length), console.log("TEST: First module:", o[0])),
                s(o),
                n(!1)
            } catch (i) {
                console.error("TEST: Error:", i),
                s({
                    error: i.message
                }),
                n(!1)
            }
        })()
    }, []), r ? e.jsxs("div", {
        style: {
            padding: "20px"
        },
        children: [e.jsx("h1", {
            children: "Test Payment Modules"
        }), e.jsx("p", {
            children: "Loading..."
        })]
    }) : e.jsxs("div", {
        style: {
            padding: "20px"
        },
        children: [e.jsx("h1", {
            children: "Test Payment Modules"
        }), t && t.error ? e.jsxs("div", {
            style: {
                color: "red"
            },
            children: [e.jsx("h2", {
                children: "Error!"
            }), e.jsx("p", {
                children: t.error
            })]
        }) : Array.isArray(t) ? e.jsxs("div", {
            style: {
                color: "green"
            },
            children: [e.jsx("h2", {
                children: "Success!"
            }), e.jsxs("p", {
                children: ["Modules loaded: ", t.length]
            }), e.jsx("pre", {
                style: {
                    background: "#f0f0f0",
                    padding: "10px",
                    overflow: "auto"
                },
                children: JSON.stringify(t, null, 2)
            })]
        }) : e.jsxs("div", {
            style: {
                color: "orange"
            },
            children: [e.jsx("h2", {
                children: "Unexpected data type"
            }), e.jsx("p", {
                children: "Data is not an array"
            }), e.jsx("pre", {
                style: {
                    background: "#f0f0f0",
                    padding: "10px",
                    overflow: "auto"
                },
                children: JSON.stringify(t, null, 2)
            })]
        })]
    })
}

function Tt({path: t, component: s}) {
    const {user: r, isLoading: n} = ks();
    return n ? e.jsx(bt, {
        path: t,
        children: () => e.jsx("div", {
            className: "flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen",
            children: e.jsx(Xt, {
                className: "h-8 w-8 animate-spin text-border"
            })
        })
    }) : r ? e.jsx(bt, {
        path: t,
        component: s
    }) : e.jsx(bt, {
        path: t,
        children: () => e.jsx(WS, {
            to: "/login"
        })
    })
}
const KK = () => {
        const {toast: t} = rt(),
            [s, r] = h.useState(!1),
            [n, a] = h.useState(!1),
            {data: i, isLoading: o, refetch: l} = Te({
                queryKey: ["/api/google-merchant/stats"],
                queryFn: () => fetch("/api/google-merchant/stats").then(y => y.json())
            }),
            c = async () => {
                try {
                    r(!0),
                    t({
                        title: "Generando feed",
                        description: "Creando archivo XML para Google Merchant Center..."
                    });
                    const y = await fetch("/api/google-merchant/feed.xml");
                    if (!y.ok)
                        throw new Error("Error al generar el feed");
                    const g = await y.blob(),
                        x = window.URL.createObjectURL(g),
                        b = document.createElement("a");
                    b.href = x,
                    b.download = `google-merchant-feed-${new Date().toISOString().split("T")[0]}.xml`,
                    document.body.appendChild(b),
                    b.click(),
                    document.body.removeChild(b),
                    window.URL.revokeObjectURL(x),
                    t({
                        title: "Feed descargado",
                        description: "El archivo XML se ha descargado correctamente"
                    })
                } catch (y) {
                    console.error("Error al descargar feed:", y),
                    t({
                        title: "Error",
                        description: "No se pudo descargar el feed XML",
                        variant: "destructive"
                    })
                } finally {
                    r(!1)
                }
            },
            d = async () => {
                try {
                    const y = await fetch("/api/google-merchant/preview");
                    if (!y.ok)
                        throw new Error("Error al generar vista previa");

                        x = window.open();
                    x && (x.document.write(`
          <html>
            <head>
              <title>Vista previa - Google Merchant Feed</title>

                body { font-family: monospace; padding: 20px; }

              </style>
            </head>
            <body>
              <h2>Vista previa del Feed XML (primeros 10 productos)</h2>
              <pre>${









                    g.replace(/</g, "&lt;").replace(/>/g, "&gt;")}</pre>
            </body>
          </html>
        `


                    ), x.document.close())
                } catch (y) {

                        description: "No se pudo mostrar la vista previa",

                    })

                                                }), e.jsx(Et, {
                                                    checked: G.active,
                                                    onCheckedChange: se => Pe(G.id, se)
                                                }), e.jsx(_, {
                                                    variant: "outline",
                                                    size: "sm",
                                                    onClick: () => k(G.id),
                                                    className: "text-red-600 hover:text-red-700",
                                                    children: e.jsx(Jt, {
                                                        className: "h-4 w-4"
                                                    })
                                                })]
                                            })]
                                        })
                                    }, G.id)), o.length === 0 && e.jsx("p", {
                                        className: "text-center text-muted-foreground py-8",
                                        children: "No hay programaciones configuradas"
                                    })]
                                })
                            })]
                        })]
                    }), e.jsx(ze, {
                        value: "monitor",
                        className: "space-y-6",
                        children: e.jsx(YK, {
                            importHistory: C || [],
                            onControlImport: Z,
                            onDeleteAllHistory: de
                        })
                    }), e.jsx(ze, {
                        value: "config",
                        className: "space-y-6",
                        children: e.jsxs("div", {
                            className: "grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6",
                            children: [e.jsxs($, {
                                children: [e.jsx(ne, {
                                    children: e.jsx(ae, {
                                        children: "Configuración del Sistema"
                                    })
                                }), e.jsxs(V, {
                                    className: "space-y-4",
                                    children: [e.jsxs("div", {
                                        className: "flex items-center space-x-2",
                                        children: [e.jsx(Et, {
                                            id: "autoRefreshEnabled",
                                            checked: p,
                                            onCheckedChange: v
                                        }), e.jsxs(q, {
                                            htmlFor: "autoRefreshEnabled",
                                            children: ["Actualización automática de datos", e.jsx("span", {
                                                className: "block text-xs text-muted-foreground",
                                                children: "Actualiza automáticamente el historial y estado de las importaciones"
                                            })]

                                                className: "h-3 w-3 mr-1"
                                            }), "Limpiar Estadísticas"]
                                        })]
                                    })
                                }), e.jsx(V, {
                                    children: A && e.jsxs("div", {

                                                    children: A.totalImports || 0
                                                }), e.jsx("p", {
                                                    className: "text-sm text-muted-foreground",
                                                    children: "Importaciones totales"
                                                })]
                                            }), e.jsxs("div", {
                                                className: "text-center",

                                                    className: "text-2xl font-bold",
                                                    children: [A.successRate || 0, "%"]
                                                }), e.jsx("p", {
                                                    className: "text-sm text-muted-foreground",
                                                    children: "Tasa de éxito"
                                                })]
                                            })]
                                        }), e.jsx(wa, {}), e.jsxs("div", {
                                            className: "space-y-2",
                                            children: [e.jsxs("p", {
                                                className: "text-sm",
                                                children: [e.jsx("span", {
                                                    className: "font-medium",
                                                    children: "Última importación:"
                                                }), " ", A.lastImport ? new Date(A.lastImport).toLocaleString() : "Nunca"]
                                            }), e.jsxs("p", {
                                                className: "text-sm",
                                                children: [e.jsx("span", {
                                                    className: "font-medium",
                                                    children: "Próxima programada:"
                                                }), " ", A.nextScheduled ? new Date(A.nextScheduled).toLocaleString() : "No programada"]
                                            })]
                                        })]
                                    })
                                })]
                            })]
                        })
                    })]
                })]
            })]
        })
    };
function RM({content: t, onChange: s, placeholder: r, className: n}) {
    const a = h.useRef(null),
        [i, o] = h.useState(!1),
        [l, c] = h.useState(t);
    h.useEffect(() => {
        if (c(t), a.current && a.current.innerHTML !== t) {
            const p = di.sanitize(t, {
                ALLOWED_TAGS: ["p", "br", "strong", "em", "u", "h1", "h2", "h3", "h4", "h5", "h6", "ul", "ol", "li", "a", "img", "div"],
                ALLOWED_ATTR: ["href", "target", "rel", "src", "alt", "style", "class"],
                ALLOWED_URI_REGEXP: /^(?:(?:(?:f|ht)tps?|mailto|tel|callto|cid|xmpp|data):|[^a-z]|[a-z+.\-]+(?:[^a-z+.\-:]|$))/i
            });
            a.current.innerHTML = p
        }
    }, [t]);
    const d = () => {
            if (a.current) {
                const p = a.current.innerHTML;
                c(p),
                s(p)
            }
        },
        u = p => {
            if (c(p), s(p), a.current) {
                const v = di.sanitize(p, {
                    ALLOWED_TAGS: ["p", "br", "strong", "em", "u", "h1", "h2", "h3", "h4", "h5", "h6", "ul", "ol", "li", "a", "img", "div"],
                    ALLOWED_ATTR: ["href", "target", "rel", "src", "alt", "style", "class"],
                    ALLOWED_URI_REGEXP: /^(?:(?:(?:f|ht)tps?|mailto|tel|callto|cid|xmpp|data):|[^a-z]|[a-z+.\-]+(?:[^a-z+.\-:]|$))/i
                });
                a.current.innerHTML = v
            }
        },
        m = (p, v) => {
            var N;
            try {
                document.queryCommandSupported && document.queryCommandSupported(p) ? document.execCommand(p, !1, v) : f(p, v)
            } catch (w) {
                console.warn("Error executing command:", p, w),
                f(p, v)
            }
            (N = a.current) == null || N.focus(),
            d()
        },
        f = (p, v) => {
            if (!a.current)
                return;
            const N = window.getSelection();
            if (!N || N.rangeCount === 0)
                return;
            const w = N.getRangeAt(0);
            switch (p) {
            case "bold":
                y("strong");
                break;
            case "italic":
                y("em");
                break;
            case "underline":
                y("u");
                break;
            case "createLink":
                if (v) {
                    const C = document.createElement("a");
                    C.href = v,
                    C.target = "_blank",
                    C.rel = "noopener noreferrer";
                    try {
                        w.surroundContents(C)
                    } catch {
                        w.deleteContents(),
                        w.insertNode(C)
                    }
                }
                break;
            case "insertImage":
                if (v) {
                    const C = document.createElement("img");
                    C.src = v,
                    C.style.maxWidth = "100%",
                    C.style.height = "auto",
                    w.insertNode(C)
                }
                break;
            case "insertUnorderedList":
                g("ul");
                break;
            default:
                if (p.startsWith("justify")) {
                    const C = p.replace("justify", "").toLowerCase(),
                        S = document.createElement("div");
                    S.style.textAlign = C === "left" ? "left" : C === "center" ? "center" : "right";
                    try {
                        w.surroundContents(S)
                    } catch {
                        w.deleteContents(),
                        w.insertNode(S)
                    }
                }
                break
            }
        },
        y = p => {
            const v = window.getSelection();
            if (!v || v.rangeCount === 0)
                return;
            const N = v.getRangeAt(0),
                w = N.toString();
            if (w) {
                const C = document.createElement(p);
                C.textContent = w,
                N.deleteContents(),
                N.insertNode(C)
            }
        },
        g = p => {
            const v = window.getSelection();
            if (!v || v.rangeCount === 0)
                return;
            const N = v.getRangeAt(0),
                w = N.toString();
            if (w) {
                const C = document.createElement(p),
                    S = document.createElement("li");
                S.textContent = w,
                C.appendChild(S),
                N.deleteContents(),
                N.insertNode(C)
            }
        },
        x = () => {
            const p = prompt("Ingrese la URL:");
            p && m("createLink", p)
        },
        b = () => {
            const p = prompt("Ingrese la URL de la imagen:");
            p && m("insertImage", p)
        },
        j = [{
            icon: JO,
            command: "bold",
            title: "Negrita"
        }, {
            icon: p5,
            command: "italic",
            title: "Cursiva"
        }, {
            icon: _5,
            command: "underline",
            title: "Subrayado"
        }, {
            icon: YO,
            command: "justifyLeft",
            title: "Alinear izquierda"
        }, {
            icon: KO,
            command: "justifyCenter",
            title: "Centrar"
        }, {
            icon: QO,
            command: "justifyRight",
            title: "Alinear derecha"
        }, {
            icon: yp,
            command: "insertUnorderedList",
            title: "Lista"
        }];
    return e.jsx("div", {
        className: ue("border rounded-lg overflow-hidden", n),
        children: e.jsxs(ls, {
            defaultValue: "visual",
            className: "w-full",
            children: [e.jsxs(es, {
                className: "grid w-full grid-cols-2",
                children: [e.jsx(Ve, {
                    value: "visual",
                    children: "Editor Visual"
                }), e.jsx(Ve, {
                    value: "html",
                    children: "Código HTML"
                })]
            }), e.jsxs(ze, {
                value: "visual",
                className: "m-0",
                children: [e.jsxs("div", {
                    className: "border-b bg-gray-50 p-2 flex flex-wrap gap-1",
                    children: [j.map(p => e.jsx(_, {
                        variant: "ghost",
                        size: "sm",
                        className: "h-8 w-8 p-0",
                        onClick: () => m(p.command),
                        title: p.title,
                        type: "button",
                        children: e.jsx(p.icon, {
                            className: "h-4 w-4"
                        })
                    }, p.command)), e.jsx("div", {
                        className: "w-px h-6 bg-gray-300 mx-1"
                    }), e.jsx(_, {
                        variant: "ghost",
                        size: "sm",
                        className: "h-8 w-8 p-0",
                        onClick: x,
                        title: "Insertar enlace",
                        type: "button",
                        children: e.jsx(g5, {
                            className: "h-4 w-4"
                        })
                    }), e.jsx(_, {
                        variant: "ghost",
                        size: "sm",
                        className: "h-8 w-8 p-0",
                        onClick: b,
                        title: "Insertar imagen",
                        type: "button",
                        children: e.jsx($s, {
                            className: "h-4 w-4"
                        })
                    }), e.jsx("div", {
                        className: "w-px h-6 bg-gray-300 mx-1"
                    }), e.jsxs("select", {
                        onChange: p => m("formatBlock", p.target.value),
                        className: "h-8 px-2 text-sm border rounded",
                        defaultValue: "",
                        children: [e.jsx("option", {
                            value: "",
                            children: "Formato"
                        }), e.jsx("option", {
                            value: "h1",
                            children: "Título 1"
                        }), e.jsx("option", {
                            value: "h2",
                            children: "Título 2"
                        }), e.jsx("option", {
                            value: "h3",
                            children: "Título 3"
                        }), e.jsx("option", {
                            value: "p",
                            children: "Párrafo"
                        })]
                    })]
                }), e.jsxs("div", {
                    className: "relative",
                    children: [e.jsx("div", {
                        ref: a,
                        contentEditable: !0,
                        onInput: d,
                        onFocus: () => o(!0),
                        onBlur: () => o(!1),
                        className: ue("min-h-[300px] p-4 outline-none prose prose-sm max-w-none", "focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:ring-inset", !t && !i && "text-gray-400"),
                        style: {
                            whiteSpace: "pre-wrap",
                            wordWrap: "break-word"
                        },
                        suppressContentEditableWarning: !0
                    }), !t && !i && e.jsx("div", {
                        className: "absolute top-4 left-4 text-gray-400 pointer-events-none",
                        children: r || "Escriba el contenido aquí..."
                    })]
                })]
            }), e.jsx(ze, {
                value: "html",
                className: "m-0",
                children: e.jsx(Ut, {
                    value: l,
                    onChange: p => u(p.target.value),
                    placeholder: "Ingrese el código HTML aquí...",
                    className: "min-h-[400px] font-mono text-sm border-0 rounded-none resize-none"
                })
            })]
        })
    })
}
function ZK() {
    const [t, s] = h.useState("pages"),
        [r, n] = h.useState(null),
        [a, i] = h.useState(null),
        [o, l] = h.useState({}),
        [c, d] = h.useState({}),
        [u, m] = h.useState(!1),
        [f, y] = h.useState(!1),
        {toast: g} = rt(),
        x = fr(),
        {data: b, isLoading: j} = Te({
            queryKey: ["/api/admin/cms/pages"],
            queryFn: async () => {
                const A = await fetch("/api/admin/cms/pages", {
                    credentials: "include"
                });
                if (!A.ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al cargar páginas");
                return A.json()
            }
        }),
        {data: p, isLoading: v} = Te({
            queryKey: ["/api/admin/cms/footer-blocks"],
            queryFn: async () => {
                const A = await fetch("/api/admin/cms/footer-blocks", {
                    credentials: "include"
                });
                if (!A.ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al cargar bloques");
                return A.json()
            }
        }),
        {data: N, isLoading: w, error: C} = Te({
            queryKey: ["/api/cms/site-settings"],
            queryFn: async () => {
                const A = await fetch("/api/cms/site-settings", {
                    credentials: "include"
                });
                if (!A.ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al cargar configuraciones");
                return A.json()
            }
        }),
        S = async () => {
            try {
                const A = r ? "PUT" : "POST",
                    I = r ? `/api/admin/cms/pages/${r.id}` : "/api/admin/cms/pages";
                if (!(await fetch(I, {
                    method: A,
                    headers: {
                        "Content-Type": "application/json"
                    },
                    credentials: "include",
                    body: JSON.stringify(o)
                })).ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al guardar página");
                x.invalidateQueries({
                    queryKey: ["/api/admin/cms/pages"]
                }),
                n(null),
                l({}),
                m(!1),
                g({
                    title: r ? "Página actualizada exitosamente" : "Página creada exitosamente"
                })
            } catch {
                g({
                    title: "Error al guardar página",
                    variant: "destructive"
                })
            }
        },
        T = async A => {
            try {
                if (!(await fetch(`/api/admin/cms/pages/${A}`, {
                    method: "DELETE",
                    credentials: "include"
                })).ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al eliminar página");
                x.invalidateQueries({
                    queryKey: ["/api/admin/cms/pages"]
                }),
                g({
                    title: "Página eliminada exitosamente"
                })
            } catch {
                g({
                    title: "Error al eliminar página",
                    variant: "destructive"
                })
            }
        },
        L = async () => {
            try {
                const A = a ? "PUT" : "POST",
                    I = a ? `/api/admin/cms/footer-blocks/${a.id}` : "/api/admin/cms/footer-blocks";
                if (!(await fetch(I, {
                    method: A,
                    headers: {
                        "Content-Type": "application/json"
                    },
                    credentials: "include",
                    body: JSON.stringify(c)
                })).ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al guardar bloque");
                x.invalidateQueries({
                    queryKey: ["/api/admin/cms/footer-blocks"]
                }),
                i(null),
                d({}),
                y(!1),
                g({
                    title: a ? "Bloque actualizado exitosamente" : "Bloque creado exitosamente"
                })
            } catch {
                g({
                    title: "Error al guardar bloque",
                    variant: "destructive"
                })
            }
        },
        H = async A => {
            try {
                if (!(await fetch(`/api/admin/cms/footer-blocks/${A}`, {
                    method: "DELETE",
                    credentials: "include"
                })).ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al eliminar bloque");
                x.invalidateQueries({
                    queryKey: ["/api/admin/cms/footer-blocks"]
                }),
                g({
                    title: "Bloque eliminado exitosamente"
                })
            } catch {
                g({
                    title: "Error al eliminar bloque",
                    variant: "destructive"
                })
            }
        },
        F = async (A, I) => {
            try {
                if (!(await fetch(`/api/cms/site-settings/${A}`, {
                    method: "PUT",
                    headers: {
                        "Content-Type": "application/json"
                    },
                    credentials: "include",
                    body: JSON.stringify({
                        value: I
                    })
                })).ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al actualizar configuración");
                x.invalidateQueries({
                    queryKey: ["/api/cms/site-settings"]
                }),
                g({
                    title: "Configuración actualizada exitosamente"
                })
            } catch {
                g({
                    title: "Error al actualizar configuración",
                    variant: "destructive"
                })
            }
        };
    return e.jsxs("div", {
        className: "flex min-h-screen bg-background",
        children: [e.jsx(Ls, {
            activeTab: "admin_cms"
        }), e.jsxs("div", {
            className: "flex-1 p-6",
            children: [e.jsx("h1", {
                className: "text-3xl font-bold mb-8",
                children: "Sistema de Gestión de Contenido"
            }), e.jsxs("div", {
                className: "flex space-x-2 mb-6 border-b pb-4",
                children: [e.jsx(_, {
                    variant: t === "pages" ? "default" : "outline",
                    onClick: () => s("pages"),
                    children: "Páginas"
                }), e.jsx(_, {
                    variant: t === "footer" ? "default" : "outline",
                    onClick: () => s("footer"),
                    children: "Footer"
                }), e.jsx(_, {
                    variant: t === "settings" ? "default" : "outline",
                    onClick: () => s("settings"),
                    children: "Configuraciones"
                })]
            }), t === "pages" && e.jsxs("div", {
                className: "space-y-6",
                children: [e.jsxs("div", {
                    className: "flex justify-between items-center",
                    children: [e.jsx("h2", {
                        className: "text-2xl font-semibold",
                        children: "Gestión de Páginas"
                    }), e.jsxs(_, {
                        onClick: () => {
                            m(!0),
                            l({
                                title: "",
                                slug: "",
                                content: "",
                                metaDescription: "",
                                isPublished: !0,
                                isEditable: !0,
                                pageType: "static"
                            })
                        },
                        children: [e.jsx(nn, {
                            className: "w-4 h-4 mr-2"
                        }), "Nueva Página"]
                    })]
                }), e.jsxs("div", {
                    className: "grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6",
                    children: [e.jsxs($, {
                        children: [e.jsx(ne, {
                            children: e.jsx(ae, {
                                children: "Páginas Existentes"
                            })
                        }), e.jsx(V, {
                            className: "space-y-4",
                            children: j ? e.jsx("div", {
                                children: "Cargando páginas..."
                            }) : b == null ? void 0 : b.map(A => e.jsxs("div", {
                                className: "flex items-center justify-between p-4 border rounded-lg",
                                children: [e.jsxs("div", {
                                    className: "space-y-1",
                                    children: [e.jsx("h3", {
                                        className: "font-medium",
                                        children: A.title
                                    }), e.jsxs("p", {
                                        className: "text-sm text-muted-foreground",
                                        children: ["/", A.slug]
                                    }), e.jsxs("div", {
                                        className: "flex gap-2",
                                        children: [e.jsx(ve, {
                                            variant: A.isPublished ? "default" : "secondary",
                                            children: A.isPublished ? "Publicada" : "Borrador"
                                        }), e.jsx(ve, {
                                            variant: "outline",
                                            children: A.pageType
                                        })]
                                    })]
                                }), e.jsxs("div", {
                                    className: "flex gap-2",
                                    children: [e.jsx(_, {
                                        size: "sm",
                                        variant: "outline",
                                        onClick: () => {
                                            n(A),
                                            l(A),
                                            m(!1)
                                        },
                                        children: e.jsx(on, {
                                            className: "w-4 h-4"
                                        })
                                    }), A.isEditable && e.jsx(_, {
                                        size: "sm",
                                        variant: "destructive",
                                        onClick: () => T(A.id),
                                        children: e.jsx(Jt, {
                                            className: "w-4 h-4"
                                        })
                                    })]
                                })]
                            }, A.id))
                        })]
                    }), (r || u) && e.jsxs($, {
                        children: [e.jsx(ne, {
                            children: e.jsx(ae, {
                                children: u ? "Nueva Página" : `Editando: ${r == null ? void 0 : r.title}`
                            })
                        }), e.jsxs(V, {
                            className: "space-y-4",

function XK() {
    const [, t] = mt(),
        [s, r] = h.useState(null),
        [n, a] = h.useState(""),
        [i, o] = h.useState(!1),
        l = () => {
            var f;
            if (!s)
                return;
            if (o(!0), console.log("🚨 PÁGINA INTERMEDIA - Enviando datos a Redsys"), console.log("🚨 DATOS COMPLETOS:", {
                actionUrl: s.actionUrl,
                merchantParameters: s.merchantParameters,
                signature: s.signature,
                hasFormHtml: !!s.formHtml,
                orderNumber: s.orderNumber,
                amount: s.amount
            }), s.formHtml) {
                console.log("🚨 USANDO FORMULARIO HTML DEL BACKEND");
                const y = document.createElement("div"),
                    b = new DOMParser().parseFromString(s.formHtml, "text/html").querySelector("form");
                b && y.appendChild(b.cloneNode(!0));
                const j = y.querySelector("form");
                if (j) {
                    j.style.display = "none",
                    document.body.appendChild(j),
                    console.log("🚨 FORMULARIO DEL BACKEND AÑADIDO AL DOM"),
                    console.log("- Action:", j.action),
                    console.log("- Method:", j.method),
                    console.log("- Fields count:", j.children.length);
                    const p = j.querySelector('input[name="Ds_SignatureVersion"]'),
                        v = j.querySelector('input[name="Ds_MerchantParameters"]'),
                        N = j.querySelector('input[name="Ds_Signature"]');
                    console.log("🚨 VERIFICANDO CAMPOS:"),
                    console.log("- Ds_SignatureVersion:", p == null ? void 0 : p.value),
                    console.log("- Ds_MerchantParameters length:", (f = v == null ? void 0 : v.value) == null ? void 0 : f.length),
                    console.log("- Ds_Signature:", N == null ? void 0 : N.value),
                    console.log("🚨 ENVIANDO FORMULARIO DEL BACKEND A REDSYS..."),
                    j.submit(),
                    sessionStorage.removeItem("redsysPaymentData");
                    return
                }
            }
            console.log("🚨 FALLBACK: Creando formulario manualmente");
            const c = document.createElement("form");
            c.method = "POST",
            c.action = s.actionUrl,
            c.acceptCharset = "UTF-8",
            c.enctype = "application/x-www-form-urlencoded",
            c.style.display = "none";
            const d = document.createElement("input");
            d.type = "hidden",
            d.name = "Ds_SignatureVersion",
            d.value = "HMAC_SHA256_V1",
            c.appendChild(d);

            u.type = "hidden",
            u.name = "Ds_MerchantParameters",

            m.type = "hidden",
            m.name = "Ds_Signature",

            document.body.appendChild(c),
            console.log("🚨 FORMULARIO MANUAL CREADO - Verificando campos:"),
            console.log("- Action:", c.action),
            console.log("- Method:", c.method),
            console.log("- Fields count:", c.children.length),
            console.log("- Ds_SignatureVersion:", d.value),

            sessionStorage.removeItem("redsysPaymentData")
        };
    return h.useEffect(() => {
        var d,
            u;
        const c = sessionStorage.getItem("redsysPaymentData");

            a("No se encontraron datos de pago. Redirigiendo al checkout..."),
            setTimeout(() => t("/checkout"), 3e3);

        }

                hasFormHtml: !!m.formHtml,

                className: "text-gray-600",
                children: "Preparando el pago..."
            })]
        })
    })
}
function JK() {
    const [t, s] = h.useState("pages"),
        [r, n] = h.useState(null),
        [a, i] = h.useState(null),
        [o, l] = h.useState({}),
        [c, d] = h.useState({}),
        [u, m] = h.useState(!1),
        [f, y] = h.useState(!1),
        [g, x] = h.useState({}),
        [b, j] = h.useState({}),
        {toast: p} = rt(),
        v = fr(),
        {data: N, isLoading: w} = Te({
            queryKey: ["/api/admin/cms/pages"],
            queryFn: async () => {
                const P = await fetch("/api/admin/cms/pages", {
                    credentials: "include"
                });
                if (!P.ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al cargar páginas");
                return P.json()
            }
        }),
        {data: C, isLoading: S} = Te({
            queryKey: ["/api/admin/cms/footer-blocks"],
            queryFn: async () => {
                const P = await fetch("/api/admin/cms/footer-blocks", {
                    credentials: "include"
                });
                if (!P.ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al cargar bloques");
                return P.json()
            }
        }),
        {data: T, isLoading: L} = Te({
            queryKey: ["/api/cms/site-settings"],
            queryFn: async () => {
                const P = await fetch("/api/cms/site-settings", {
                    credentials: "include"
                });
                if (!P.ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al cargar configuraciones");
                return P.json()
            }
        }),
        H = async (P, E) => {
            x(R => ({
                ...R,
                [P]: !0
            }));
            try {
                if (!(await fetch(`/api/cms/site-settings/${P}`, {
                    method: "PUT",
                    headers: {
                        "Content-Type": "application/json"
                    },
                    credentials: "include",
                    body: JSON.stringify({
                        value: E
                    })
                })).ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al actualizar configuración");
                v.invalidateQueries({
                    queryKey: ["/api/cms/site-settings"]
                }),
                j(z => {
                    const ie = {
                        ...z
                    };
                    return delete ie[P], ie
                }),
                p({
                    title: "Configuración guardada",
                    description: "Los cambios se han guardado correctamente"
                })
            } catch {
                p({
                    title: "Error al guardar",
                    description: "No se pudo guardar la configuración",
                    variant: "destructive"
                })
            } finally {
                x(R => ({
                    ...R,
                    [P]: !1
                }))
            }
        },
        F = (P, E) => {
            j(R => ({
                ...R,
                [P]: E
            }))
        },
        A = async () => {
            x(P => ({
                ...P,
                page: !0
            }));
            try {
                const P = r ? "PUT" : "POST",
                    E = r ? `/api/admin/cms/pages/${r.id}` : "/api/admin/cms/pages";
                if (!(await fetch(E, {
                    method: P,
                    headers: {
                        "Content-Type": "application/json"
                    },
                    credentials: "include",
                    body: JSON.stringify(o)
                })).ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al guardar página");
                v.invalidateQueries({
                    queryKey: ["/api/admin/cms/pages"]
                }),
                n(null),
                l({}),
                m(!1),
                p({
                    title: r ? "Página actualizada" : "Página creada"
                })
            } catch {
                p({
                    title: "Error al guardar página",
                    variant: "destructive"
                })
            } finally {
                x(P => ({
                    ...P,
                    page: !1
                }))
            }
        },
        I = async () => {
            x(P => ({
                ...P,
                block: !0
            }));
            try {
                const P = a ? "PUT" : "POST",
                    E = a ? `/api/admin/cms/footer-blocks/${a.id}` : "/api/admin/cms/footer-blocks";
                if (!(await fetch(E, {
                    method: P,
                    headers: {
                        "Content-Type": "application/json"
                    },
                    credentials: "include",
                    body: JSON.stringify(c)
                })).ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al guardar bloque");
                v.invalidateQueries({
                    queryKey: ["/api/admin/cms/footer-blocks"]
                }),
                i(null),
                d({}),
                y(!1),
                p({
                    title: a ? "Bloque actualizado" : "Bloque creado"
                })
            } catch {
                p({
                    title: "Error al guardar bloque",
                    variant: "destructive"
                })
            } finally {
                x(P => ({
                    ...P,
                    block: !1
                }))
            }
        },
        U = async P => {
            try {
                if (!(await fetch(`/api/admin/cms/footer-blocks/${P}`, {
                    method: "DELETE",
                    credentials: "include"
                })).ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al eliminar bloque");
                v.invalidateQueries({
                    queryKey: ["/api/admin/cms/footer-blocks"]
                }),
                p({
                    title: "Bloque eliminado"
                })
            } catch {
                p({
                    title: "Error al eliminar bloque",
                    variant: "destructive"
                })
            }
        },
        D = P => {
            var ie;
            const E = b[P.key] !== void 0,
                R = E ? b[P.key] : P.value,
                z = g[P.key];
            return e.jsxs("div", {
                className: "space-y-3 p-4 border rounded-lg bg-gray-50",
                children: [e.jsxs("div", {
                    className: "flex items-center justify-between",
                    children: [e.jsxs("div", {
                        className: "flex-1",
                        children: [e.jsx(q, {
                            htmlFor: P.key,
                            className: "text-sm font-medium",
                            children: P.description || P.key
                        }), e.jsxs("div", {
                            className: "flex items-center gap-2 mt-1",
                            children: [e.jsx(ve, {
                                variant: "outline",
                                className: "text-xs",
                                children: P.category
                            }), e.jsx(ve, {
                                variant: "outline",
                                className: "text-xs",
                                children: P.type
                            })]
                        })]
                    }), E && e.jsx(_, {
                        size: "sm",
                        onClick: () => H(P.key, R),
                        disabled: z,
                        className: "ml-2",
                        children: z ? e.jsx("div", {
                            className: "w-4 h-4 border-2 border-white border-t-transparent rounded-full animate-spin"
                        }) : e.jsx(Nn, {
                            className: "w-4 h-4"
                        })
                    })]
                }), P.type === "boolean" ? e.jsxs("div", {
                    className: "flex items-center space-x-2",
                    children: [e.jsx(Et, {
                        id: P.key,
                        checked: R === "true",
                        onCheckedChange: O => {
                            F(P.key, O.toString())
                        },
                        disabled: z
                    }), e.jsx(q, {
                        htmlFor: P.key,
                        className: "text-sm",
                        children: R === "true" ? "Activado" : "Desactivado"
                    })]
                }) : P.type === "json" ? e.jsx(Ut, {
                    id: P.key,
                    value: R,
                    onChange: O => F(P.key, O.target.value),
                    disabled: z,
                    rows: 4,
                    className: "font-mono text-sm",
                    placeholder: "Formato JSON válido"
                }) : P.type === "email" ? e.jsx(J, {
                    id: P.key,
                    type: "email",
                    value: R,
                    onChange: O => F(P.key, O.target.value),
                    disabled: z,
                    placeholder: "correo@ejemplo.com"
                }) : e.jsx(J, {
                    id: P.key,
                    value: R,
                    onChange: O => F(P.key, O.target.value),
                    disabled: z,
                    placeholder: `Ingrese ${((ie = P.description) == null ? void 0 : ie.toLowerCase()) || P.key}`
                })]
            }, P.id)
        };
    return e.jsxs("div", {
        className: "flex min-h-screen bg-background",
        children: [e.jsx(Ls, {
            activeTab: "admin_cms"
        }), e.jsxs("div", {
            className: "flex-1 p-6",
            children: [e.jsxs("div", {
                className: "mb-8",
                children: [e.jsx("h1", {
                    className: "text-3xl font-bold mb-2",
                    children: "Sistema de Gestión de Contenido"
                }), e.jsx("p", {
                    className: "text-muted-foreground",
                    children: "Gestiona páginas, bloques del footer y configuraciones del sitio web"
                })]
            }), e.jsxs(ls, {
                value: t,
                onValueChange: s,
                className: "w-full",
                children: [e.jsxs(es, {
                    className: "grid w-full grid-cols-4",
                    children: [e.jsxs(Ve, {
                        value: "pages",
                        className: "flex items-center gap-2",
                        children: [e.jsx(gu, {
                            className: "w-4 h-4"
                        }), "Páginas"]
                    }), e.jsxs(Ve, {
                        value: "header",
                        className: "flex items-center gap-2",
                        children: [e.jsx(mr, {
                            className: "w-4 h-4"
                        }), "Header"]
                    }), e.jsxs(Ve, {
                        value: "footer",
                        className: "flex items-center gap-2",
                        children: [e.jsx(_E, {
                            className: "w-4 h-4"
                        }), "Footer"]
                    }), e.jsxs(Ve, {
                        value: "settings",
                        className: "flex items-center gap-2",
                        children: [e.jsx(Vs, {
                            className: "w-4 h-4"
                        }), "Configuraciones"]
                    })]
                }), e.jsxs(ze, {
                    value: "pages",
                    className: "space-y-6",
                    children: [e.jsxs("div", {
                        className: "flex justify-between items-center",
                        children: [e.jsx("h2", {
                            className: "text-2xl font-semibold",
                            children: "Gestión de Páginas"
                        }), e.jsxs(_, {
                            onClick: () => {
                                m(!0),
                                l({
                                    slug: "",
                                    title: "",
                                    content: "",
                                    metaDescription: "",
                                    isPublished: !1,
                                    isEditable: !0,
                                    pageType: "content"
                                })
                            },
                            children: [e.jsx(nn, {
                                className: "w-4 h-4 mr-2"
                            }), "Nueva Página"]
                        })]
                    }), e.jsxs("div", {
                        className: "grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6",
                        children: [e.jsxs($, {

                                children: e.jsx(ae, {
                                    children: "Páginas del Sitio"
                                })
                            }), e.jsx(V, {

                                    children: [e.jsxs("div", {
                                        className: "space-y-1",
                                        children: [e.jsx("h3", {

                                            children: P.title
                                        }), e.jsxs("p", {
                                            className: "text-sm text-muted-foreground",

                                            variant: P.isPublished ? "default" : "secondary",
                                            children: P.isPublished ? "Publicado" : "Borrador"
                                        })]
                                    }), e.jsx("div", {
                                        className: "flex gap-2",
                                        children: e.jsx(_, {

                                                n(P),
                                                l(P),
                                                m(!1)
                                            },
                                            children: e.jsx(on, {
                                                className: "w-4 h-4"
                                            })
                                        })
                                    })]
                                }, P.id))

                                            }),

                                        }), e.jsx(J, {

                    value: "settings",

const FY = ({clientSecret: t, sessionId: s}) => {

                        elements: n,

                        }
                    });
                    d && a({
                        title: "Error en el pago",
                        description: d.message,
                        variant: "destructive"
                    })
                } catch {
